{"type":"message","id":"e01b6d9d","parentId":"5cc8651c","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:54:28.819Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-03-19 23:54 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索以下4个道简网络核心业务领域的最新动态（2026年3月），每个领域找1-2条关键信息：\n\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成  \n4. IT运维服务\n\n要求：\n- 来源必须是2026年3月的最新信息\n- 整理成结构化笔记保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n- 内容要简洁，每条不超过100字\n- 标注信息来源和日期"}],"timestamp":1773935668817}}
{"type":"message","id":"d0c2eca8","parentId":"e01b6d9d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:54:34.333Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我作为子代理，搜索道简网络4个核心业务领域的2026年3月最新动态，然后整理成笔记保存到指定文件。\n\n我需要：\n1. 搜索4个领域的最新信息（2026年3月）\n2. 每条不超过100字\n3. 标注信息来源和日期\n4. 保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n让我先使用web-search skill来搜索这些信息。根据技能列表，我应该使用 miaoda-web-search 或 web-search skill。\n\n先读取一下web-search skill的用法。","thinkingSignature":"4430f42c23a42e7113a1d3fe189d5c1af9becc5e1f49576c5085829007070d19"},{"type":"text","text":"\n我来搜索这4个领域的2026年3月最新动态。先读取搜索工具的用法。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5kwh6cmyaptw_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":117,"output":182,"cacheRead":18914,"cacheWrite":11909,"totalTokens":31122,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0002184,"cacheRead":0.0005674199999999999,"cacheWrite":0.0014290799999999999,"total":0.00225}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773935668818}}
{"type":"message","id":"51e3681a","parentId":"d0c2eca8","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:54:34.339Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5kwh6cmyaptw_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773935674336}}
{"type":"message","id":"7de884c8","parentId":"51e3681a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:54:38.373Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我知道如何使用搜索工具了。让我搜索4个领域的最新信息。我会分别搜索每个领域，加上2026年3月的时间限定。\n\n让我执行4个搜索命令。","thinkingSignature":"7e68af7c37cc8415618be9aaee6bc45503f6d6853e7a88d6dd1ad2b5e15077b3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zd74qxnl9o4m_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026年3月 最新动态\"","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zd74qxnl9o4m_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 2026年3月 最新动态\"","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zd74qxnl9o4m_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 2026年3月 最新动态\"","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zd74qxnl9o4m_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务 2026年3月 最新动态\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":985,"output":238,"cacheRead":30652,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31875,"cost":{"input":0.00029549999999999997,"output":0.0002856,"cacheRead":0.0009195599999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00150066}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773935674338}}
